Distribution: Western Atlantic: New Foundland ( Canada ), Mexico (Gulf of Mexico ), Bermudas , Cadix, Brazil (Rio de Janeiro). Eastern Atlantic: Azores Island, Canary Islands, Madeira Islands, Gibraltar , Gulf of Guinea , Adriatic Sea, Red Sea, Gabon , Congo , Angola . Mediterranean. Indian and Pacific: Natal , Philippines , Seychelles , Sumatra, Indonesia , Malay Archipelago, Gulf of Bengal, Banda Sea, Australia , Hawaii, Alaska. Absent from South and East China seas and from the large islands of Japan . Adults are pelagic, living in depths from 7 meters to 3600 m (modified from
Calman, 1939
; Chace 1940 , 1985 ;
Pequegnat, 1970
;
Crosnier & Forest, 1973
).
